<div class="text-center">
    <img src="~/images/PinkEmpowerHer.webp" alt="EmpowerHer Health Group" class="custom-image mb-4" />

    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to EmpowerHER Health Group</h1>
    <p>
        Welcome to EmpowerHER Health Group, where women's wellness is our top priority.
        Our dedicated team provides personalized, comprehensive care tailored to your unique needs, from routine check-ups to specialized women's health services.
        In a warm and supportive environment, we focus on empowering women to take charge of their health, addressing concerns such as menstrual wellness, reproductive health, and menopause.
        Our goal is to deliver holistic care that nurtures your body, mind, and spirit.
        Join us at EmpowerHER Health Group and start your journey to optimal wellness today.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Services</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Reproductive Health</li>
        <li>Pregnancy and Parenting</li>
        <li>Menstrual and Hormonal Health</li>
        <li>Cancer Screening and Prevention</li>
        <li>Mental Health and Wellness</li>
        <li>Chronic Disease Management</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
        Embark on a journey of holistic wellness with EmpowerHER Health Group!
        We're honored you've chosen us for your women's health needs.
        Our dedicated team is here to support and empower you every step of the way.
        For questions or to schedule an appointment, please connect with us. Join our community, where women's health, wellness, and empowerment come first!
    </p>
</div>

